1&ndash;37.</li>

<li>Urofsky, Melvin I.,2022, <em>The Affirmative Action Puzzle</em>,
New York: Skyhorse Publishing.</li>

<li>U. S. Commission on Civil Rights, 2007, <em>Affirmative Action in
American Law Schools</em>, Washington, D.C.</li>

<li>Valls, Andrew, 1999, &ldquo;The Libertarian Case for Affirmative
Action,&rdquo; <em>Social Theory and Practice</em>, 25 (Summer):
299&ndash;323.</li>

<li>Van Laar, Colette, Shana Levin, and Stacey Sinclair, 2008,
&ldquo;Social Identity and Personal Identity Stereotype Threat: The
