(January): 65&ndash;80.</li>

<li>Wise, Tim, 2005, <em>Affirmative Action: Racial Preference in
Black and White</em>, New York: Routledge.</li>

<li>Wolf-Devine, Celia, 1988, &ldquo;An Inequity in Affirmative
Action,&rdquo; <em>Journal of Applied Philosophy</em>, 5 (March):
107&ndash;108.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1997, <em>Diversity and Community in the
